title: Dive
lyrics:
Until the morning meolis-sog-en
You kept reminding me about last night
Amu maldo hal su eobsneun geol
Neoga tteonan hulo nan
Feel like I’m surfing ne mam-e

Pado-e ppajil geos gat-a

Into you I wanna dive

Ne momsog-e I wanna hide

If you don’t have the answers now

Into you just let me dive



Last night in my eyes

Jeomjeom meol-eojyeo

Last night in my arms

Jab-eul suga eobsjanh-a



Ne momsog-e gogseondeul-eun

Padoga dwae naleul samkyeo

Gyesog galaanjneun geol

Tteugeoun che-on ye it keeps me live

Ne pum-e gadhyeo idaelo let me hide



Feel like I’m surfing ne mam-e

Pado-e ppajil geos gat-a

Into you I wanna dive

Ne momsog-e I wanna hide

If you don’t have the answers now

Into you just let me dive



Last night in my eyes

Jeomjeom meol-eojyeo

Last night in my arms

Jab-eul suga eobsjanh-a



Falling falling ne mamsog-e

Falling falling into your waves

Falling falling ne pado-e

Falling falling into your waves



Last night in my eyes

Jeomjeom meol-eojyeo

Last night in my arms

Jab-eul suga eobsjanh-a
